### Summary
This documentation explains how to set up Single Sign-On (SSO) integration between Amplitude and G Suite for Scholarship, Growth, and Enterprise plan customers, detailing the step-by-step process of configuring SAML application in G Suite Admin Console and uploading the IDP metadata to Amplitude.

